It should be noted that it actually was worse, given that KA memory was
produced during the Vietnam Era Inflation,  and the Arab Oil Embargo Inflation
which was followed by  the  Post-Vietnam/Oil Embargo Inflation <which ran
through Ford and Carter until the Reagan Recession, which had little effect on
the value of the dollar took hold>.

